Package: oRm
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Object-Relational Mapper for R
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: c(person("Kent", "Orr", email = "orr.kent@pawpawanalytics.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Kent Orr <orr.kent@pawpawanalytics.com>
Description: A lightweight Object-Relational Mapper (ORM) that simplifies 
    database interactions by allowing users to define table models, insert and 
    query records, and establish relationships between models without writing 
    raw SQL. Uses a combination of DBI, dbplyr, and R6 to provide compatibility 
    with most database dialects including PostgreSQL, MySQL, and SQLite.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: DBI, dbplyr, dplyr, pool, R6, rlang
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, testthat (>= 3.0.0), stevedore (>= 0.9.6),
        RSQLite, RPostgres, withr, htmltools, bslib, tibble
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Collate: 'Column.R' 'Dialect-mysql.R' 'Dialect-postgres.R' 'Dialect.R'
        'Dialect-sqlite.R' 'TableModel.R' 'Engine.R' 'Record.R'
        'Relationship.R'
URL: https://kent-orr.github.io/oRm/, https://github.com/kent-orr/oRm
VignetteBuilder: knitr
BugReports: https://github.com/kent-orr/oRm/issues
NeedsCompilation: no
Packaged: 2025-08-22 15:20:09 UTC; kent
